<item>
            <title>[PIG-556] FindQuantiles function does not report progress</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-556</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FindQuantiles does not call progress.  Most of the time this isn&apos;t an issue as it finishes quickly.  But for very large (multi-terabyte) order bys, it does not finish in the required five minutes.  This causes the whole job to fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
